g.text: EATING LOCALWhat you choose to eat and where you buy it from makes a huge difference! Here are the 3 E’s of eating local:ENVIRONMENTLess transport costsSustainable farming practicesLess pesticidesECONOMY:Money stays in local economyPreserves agriculture jobsFarm workers surviveETHICS:Food securityHumane treatment of animalsFarm workers are unionized
